        %p.paragraph Mike always has Western movies playing in the barbershop. Our DP Jerome recalled a very memorable scene in a John Wayne movie. We began explaining the scene him. Mike knew exactly the movie, Hondo, starring John Wayne, and had a copy on VHS for us to use. We ended up using that copy in the piece.
  %section.five
