      .column
        %h2.header The Perfect Song
        %p.paragraph We ended up using a song by The Peddlers, On a Clear Day You Can See Forever. It was the first song that came to mind after the day we spent shooting with Mike and never changed. When we cut the initial edit the shot in the piece that follows our customer (Dan John Miller) from his boots up the chair to his hair just happened to land on the drum fill into the organ solo. After we saw that we cut the rest of the video around that specific shot and part in the song.
