        %h2.header Story Development
        %p.paragraph The piece was created to detail a day in the life of an incredible man, who has spent most of his days cutting hair in a one-roomed barbershop. While we were filming, a 55-year-old man came in and recounted getting his first haircut from Mike right before his senior prom. It ended up taking months of visits, conversations, haircuts, and pre-production before we knew in what light we planned to tell his story.
